<h1>Download bolo</h1>

<h2>Packages</h2>

<p>If you are running Debian/Ubuntu or RHEL/CentOS, you can take advantage of pre-built packages for bolo and it's dependencies, hosted on packagecloud.

For Debian/Ubuntu:
<pre>
$ curl -s https://packagecloud.io/install/repositories/bolo/bolo/script.deb.sh | sudo bash
$ sudo apt-get install bolo dbolo bolo-collectors
</pre>

For CentOS:
<pre>
$ curl -s https://packagecloud.io/install/repositories/bolo/bolo/script.rpm.sh | sudo bash
$ sudo yum install bolo dbolo bolo-collectors</p>
</pre>

<h2>Source</h2>

<p>The current stable version of <strong>bolo</strong> (core) is <strong>0.2.20</strong>:
<a href="https://github.com/bolo/bolo/archive/v0.2.20.tar.gz">tar.gz</a> | <a href="https://github.com/bolo/bolo/archive/v0.2.20.zip">zip</a> | <a href="https://github.com/bolo/bolo/tree/v0.2.20">git</a></p>

<p>The current stable version of the <strong>bolo-collectors</strong> is <strong>0.4.13</strong>:
<a href="https://github.com/bolo/bolo-collectors/archive/v0.4.13.tar.gz">tar.gz</a> | <a href="https://github.com/bolo/bolo-collectors/archive/v0.4.13.zip">zip</a> | <a href="https://github.com/bolo/bolo-collectors/tree/v0.4.13">git</a></p>

<p>Older releases are available at <a href="https://github.com/bolo/bolo/releases">Github</a>.</p>
